        </p>
        <p>
          The platform seamlessly tracks match events in real-time and automatically distributes points to coordinate owners. This sophisticated system connects digital ownership with live sporting action, ensuring fans benefit directly from the gameplay unfolding at their claimed coordinates.
        </p>
